#: org.kde.ark.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Ark"
msgstr "Ark"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.ark.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Archiving Tool"
msgstr "Arhivēšanas rīks"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ark.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"Ark is a graphical file compression/decompression utility with support for "
"multiple formats, including tar, gzip, bzip2, rar and zip, as well as CD-ROM "
"images. Ark can be used to browse, extract, create, and modify archives."
msgstr ""
"„Ark“ ir grafisks datņu saspiešanas/atspiešanas rīks ar daudzu formātu "
"atbalstu, tostarp tar, gzip, bzip2, rar un zip, kā arī CD-ROM attēlu. „Ark“ "
"var izmantot, lai pārlūkotu, atspiestu, izveidotu un mainītu arhīvus."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ark.appdata.xml:19
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Iespējas:"

